**How were text features extracted for the machine learning models?**
Two primary methods were used: TF-IDF (Term Frequency-Inverse Document Frequency) to create sparse, frequency-based matrices, and Word2Vec to generate dense, 100-dimensional vectors that capture semantic relationships between words.

**What preprocessing steps were applied to the raw mental health text?**
The pipeline included converting text to lowercase, removing special characters and numbers using Regex, tokenizing strings, removing NLTK stopwords, and lemmatizing words to their base forms.

